<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />是因為這種考量呀<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
原來如此～<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />不過，如果要說驚喜程度的話<tag a="110" b="0" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><anim id="Hello" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<20_3 arg="8" /><delay40 />
你聽到我們講話了？<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />其實<delay8 />我們剛剛是在討論，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />要送什麼驚喜的禮物<delay8 />
給<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />呢！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />就是說呀～<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我們已經選出了幾樣禮物，<delay20 />
正想說該送哪一樣比較好<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />對了！<20_2 arg="5" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我們也向<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay20 />
徵求一些意見<delay8 />如何呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 10 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />這主意不錯呢！<20_2 arg="3" /><pageBreak /><20_3 arg="0" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，如果是你，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />收到什麼樣的驚喜禮物<delay20 />
會讓你覺得開心呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">親手做的<tag a="135" b="5" arg="0xcd00" /></message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">大分量的<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" /></message>
	<message label="003_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />塔</message>
	<message label="003_d" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">本人造型的布偶</message>
	<message label="003_e" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一百枝花朵的花束</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />果然還是親手做的禮物<delay8 /><20_2 arg="7" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />比較有誠意，真不錯呢！<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="5" /><20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />既然這麼決定了，<delay20 />
那我們就趕快準備吧！</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />說的也是呢！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />那我們<delay8 />先決定要怎麼設計<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
再收集材料<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />製作禮物的時候，<20_2 arg="3" />我們還可以聊聊天<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
然後休息時，就喝茶配蛋糕<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />我開始覺得好期待喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />果然是這個！<delay40 /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />說到驚喜……<delay8 />震撼程度可是<delay8 />很重要的！<delay20 />
所以得做個超大分量的才行！
<20_3 arg="5" /><20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然決定了，<delay20 />
那我們就趕快準備吧！</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我們好好大顯身手，<20_2 arg="4" />做出最棒的成品吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />對了！<delay8 />要不要來我家<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />一起準備呢？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我最近<delay8 />買了一個<delay8 />非常厲害的打蛋器喔，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
真希望讓你看看<delay8 />它的優秀性能<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />哇～<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />我剛好也買了<delay20 />
最新款的橡皮刮刀喔～<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />它的彈性跟舊款的可是大不相同！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我想趁這個機會試試看，<delay20 />
那我就把它帶去你家囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />就算只是把玻璃杯一層層疊高起來，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
也會讓人有種奢華的感覺呢。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="5" /><20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />這樣需要很多玻璃杯，<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />如果只用我家裡有的杯子，<delay20 />
說不定不夠呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Assent" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />那我也把<20_2 arg="4" />家裡所有的玻璃杯<delay20 />
全都帶來！<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay40 />
可以拜託你當<delay8 />倒飲料的人嗎？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />哇！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />可以嗎？<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我一直很想試試看……<delay20 />
從塔的最頂端<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />倒下飲料呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />這主意不錯耶～<delay40 /><20_2 arg="7" />
如果收到和自己長得<delay20 />
一模一樣的布偶，<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />一定會嚇一跳吧！
<20_3 arg="5" /><20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />既然決定了，<delay20 />
那我們就趕快準備吧！</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />那麼<20_2 arg="4" />我就去<delay20 />準備材料喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />再來，<delay8 />我還想打個版型，<delay20 />
如果有本人的照片就好了<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那樣的話，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />我就去拍照吧。<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Assent" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我可是<delay8 />很擅長拍照的喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="HappyDance" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />花束啊……真棒呢！<delay40 /><20_2 arg="7" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />可是，<delay8 />要怎樣才能蒐集到<delay20 />
一百枝花朵呢？</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />說的也是呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<20_3 arg="5" /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />我們現在開始種就好了呀！<anim id="Aha" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Assent" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />需要種子的話，<delay8 />我再帶過來吧。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />真是個好點子呢～<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />我們可要偷偷地種，<delay20 />
別讓本人發現囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay40 />
謝謝你的建議！<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />讓我們受益良多呢～<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哇～<delay8 />真不錯呢～<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Love" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />在那樣的氣氛下<delay8 />看自己喜歡的書，<delay20 />
真是太棒了～</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />是啊！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />在夜幕低垂時<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
坐在房間的窗戶旁，<delay8 />點著一盞燭火<delay8 />看書……<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />會非常有氣氛喔～<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />，<delay8 />
我也想問你有沒有推薦的看書環境呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />如果<20_2 arg="3" />問我的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我還是喜歡<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />在滿天星星的夜空下，<delay20 />
點著提燈<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />看書呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />哇～<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />感覺也很棒呢～<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我來試一次看看好了？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />可以的話，<20_2 arg="3" />要不要一起試試看呢？<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />在星空下<delay8 />開讀書會！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />哇！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />真是個好點子呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />不過<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />要是星星沒有出現，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />該怎麼辦呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />那到時<20_2 arg="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我們就帶上茶和餅乾，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />一起享用吧。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />嗯～<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />這麼一來，<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />就變成普通的茶會了呢。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />一起來祈禱<20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />那天會出現星星吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />至於細節，我們就<delay20 />
下次再來討論喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />我知道了。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />那就等<delay8 />你方便的時候，<delay20 />
我再拿去你家吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />非常感謝你～<20_2 arg="4" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />話說回來，<delay8 />我一直很在意<delay40 />
你說的那個「<tag a="110" b="5" />」<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />你從以前開始就是那樣說話的嗎？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵！<20_2 arg="3" />你發現了嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />不愧是<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />只要說話方式一變，<delay20 />自己的意識也會改變，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />這樣很不錯喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />哇，<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />原來是這樣啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />難怪我覺得……<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />你今天<delay8 />有點不太一樣，特別吸引人呢。<anim id="Blushing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />那個～<delay40 />
我想問，<delay20 />我能不能也<delay8 />
用用看那個說話方式呢？</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />當然<20_2 arg="3" />可以啊！<delay frames="60" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
能跟你用一樣的方式說話，<delay8 />我好開心喔！</message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />非常感謝你！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />那麼我就馬上來用用看<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />關於剛剛的那件事，<delay20 />
就拜託你囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="207" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />我知道了。<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />那我再把東西拿去你家喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 />我們的口頭禪<delay20 />
變得一樣了耶，<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
真是太棒了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
